## Executive Summary

Version 1.0.0 introduces the first release of the Payment Gateway Dashboard. This release includes a complete payment management workflow, webhook configuration and logging, authentication, support module, user profile management, application settings, responsive user interface, and comprehensive technical documentation.

## Version 1.0.0

### Release Highlights

- Initial application release
- Responsive dashboard
- Complete payment workflow
- Webhook configuration and logging
- Authentication module
- Support management
- User profile management
- Settings module
- Documentation set

